title: The Creation of Israel and Conspiracy Theories Iakovos Alhadeff
description: This essay offers a brief and simple presentation of the circumstances under which Israel was created. The aim of the essay is to help the well intentioned and confused reader realize that the creation of Israel was not the result of a world conspiracy, but rather the country was created in exactly the same way that all other countries were created. That is with a mix of diplomacy, battle and blood.
